### [Psalms Chapter 115](../../../bib/kjv/psa115.htm#001.md)

[Psalms](../../../bib/kjv/psa001.htm#001.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_000">psa 115:0</span></span>

Overview

[Psa 115:1](../../../bib/kjv/psa115.htm#001.md), Because God is truly
glorious, [Psa 115:4](../../../bib/kjv/psa115.htm#004.md), and idols are
vanity, [Psa 115:9](../../../bib/kjv/psa115.htm#009.md), he exhorts to
confidence in God; [Psa 115:12](../../../bib/kjv/psa115.htm#012.md), God is
to be blessed for his blessings.

